      </p>
      <p class="positioning-statement">
        This knowledge system tracks theoretical models (TAM, ECM, ECT), their constructs and relationships, literature findings, and the evolution of research questions through the doctoral journey.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="quick-links">
      <h2>Quick Links</h2>
      <div class="link-grid">
        <a href="/models/" class="link-card">
          <span class="link-icon">üìö</span>
          <span class="link-title">Models</span>
