        </a>
        <a href="/constructs/" class="link-card">
          <span class="link-icon">üß†</span>
          <span class="link-title">Constructs</span>
          <span class="link-desc">Definitions, measurement scales, sources</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/diary/" class="link-card">
          <span class="link-icon">üìì</span>
          <span class="link-title">Diary</span>
          <span class="link-desc">Daily reflections, tags, linked constructs</span>
